sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Human
    participant UI as replicata UI tab
    participant Server as replicata HTTP server<br/>(127.0.0.1:3589)
    participant Replicata as replicata core<br/>(Node.js)
    participant RealApp as Real ChatGPT<br/>(tab in Chrome)
    participant Disk as ~/.replicata/tags/*.json

    Note over Human,Disk: Installation (on replicata start)
    Replicata->>Disk: read existing tags (if any)
    Replicata->>RealApp: install __replicataResolveTag + __replicataHighlightMatches<br/>(addInitScript + evaluate, idempotent)
    Replicata->>RealApp: install dom-watch MutationObserver<br/>(debounced 750ms → __replicataDomChanged)

    Note over Human,Disk: Picking a tag
    Human->>UI: click "+ Tag element"
    UI->>Server: POST /tag/start (long-poll)
    Server->>Replicata: startPicker()
    Replicata->>RealApp: Overlay.setInspectMode (searchForNode)
    Human->>RealApp: click element in real app
    RealApp-)Replicata: Overlay.inspectNodeRequested<br/>(backendNodeId)
    Replicata->>RealApp: DOM.resolveNode → Runtime.callFunctionOn<br/>(element-info helper)
    RealApp-->>Replicata: { tagName, text, attrs,<br/>testId?, ariaLabel?, role?,<br/>classPath, nthChildPath, cssPath }
    Replicata->>RealApp: Overlay.setInspectMode(none) + disable
    Replicata-->>Server: PickedElement
    Server-->>UI: PickedElement
    UI->>UI: show naming form w/ suggested name
    Human->>UI: enters name, clicks Save
    UI->>Server: POST /tag/name { name, picked }
    Server->>Replicata: createTag(name, picked)
    Replicata->>Disk: save JSON (schemaVersion: 1)
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataSetTags([..., new tag])<br/>(refresh event-tap cache)
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataResolveTag(locator) (verify)
    Replicata-->>Server: Tag w/ resolution
    Server-->>UI: Tag w/ resolution
    UI->>UI: render tag in list

    Note over Human,Disk: Verify on reload / DOM change
    RealApp-)Replicata: __replicataDomChanged() (debounced)
    Replicata->>Replicata: throttled scheduleVerify<br/>(2s min interval)
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataResolveTag(locator) per tag
    RealApp-->>Replicata: { status, matchedBy, count }
    Replicata->>Replicata: resolutionByTagId.set(id, result)
    UI->>Server: GET /tags (polling every 1.5s)
    Server-->>UI: tags w/ resolution + paired status
    UI->>UI: render ✓ / ⚠ / ×N per tag

    Note over Human,Disk: Hover to highlight
    Human->>UI: hover tag row
    UI->>Server: POST /tag/:id/highlight
    Server->>Replicata: highlightTag(id)
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataHighlightMatches(locator)<br/>(draws DOM overlays on each match, rAF-tracked)
    Human->>UI: move mouse away
    UI->>Server: POST /highlight/clear
    Server->>Replicata: clearHighlight()
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataHideHighlights()
